{"declarations":[{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Tactic/CategoryTheory/CategoryStar.html#Mathlib.Tactic.CategoryStar.«termCategory*__»\"><span class=\"name\">Mathlib</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">CategoryStar</span>.<span class=\"name\">«termCategory*__»</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.ParserDescr\">Lean.ParserDescr</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The syntax `Category* C` creates a new distinct implicit universe parameter `v`, placed\njust before any parameters appearing in `C` and its type, and elaborates to `Category.{v} C`.\n","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/CategoryTheory/CategoryStar.html#Mathlib.Tactic.CategoryStar.«termCategory*__»","kind":"def","line":49,"name":"Mathlib.Tactic.CategoryStar.«termCategory*__»","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/Tactic/CategoryTheory/CategoryStar.lean#L49-L59"}}],"imports":["Init","Lean.Util.CollectLevelParams","Lean.Elab.Term.TermElabM","Mathlib.Init","Mathlib.Lean.Elab.Term","Batteries.Data.Array.Basic"],"instances":[],"name":"Mathlib.Tactic.CategoryTheory.CategoryStar"}